nodes.text: Tenn  was a Human male sergeant of the Galactic Republic stationed on the war torn world of Balmorra around 3642 BBY. During that same year, he tasked a traveling Republic hero to kill a Colicoid queen in an overrun Balmorran resistance base that was causing issues to the Republic military front on the planet with insurances and was known for lightning fast strikes.
Tenn first appeared in the 2011 BioWare MMORPG Star Wars: The Old Republic for Republic classes in the heroic mission Local Predators.
